# on, [[up to]], [[down to]] (someone or something)
#: {{uxi|fr|mettre quelque chose '''sur le compte de''' quelqu'un, imputer quelque chose à quelqu'un|to attribute something to someone, to ascribe something to someone}}
#: {{uxi|fr|mettre quelque chose '''sur le compte de''' quelque chose|to put something down to something, to [[chalk up to|chalk something up to something]]}}
#: {{uxi|fr|J'ai mis ça '''sur le compte de''' la fatigue.|I put that down to tiredness.}}
# [[about]]
#: {{syn|fr|au sujet de}}
#: {{uxi|fr|Je me suis trompé '''sur son compte'''.|I was mistaken about him, I was wrong about him.}}

====Usage notes====
* Does not translate as {{m|en|on account of}}.
* Not to be confused with {{m|fr|pour le compte de}}.

